     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>The Books to the Reader.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>THis debt is due vpon Doomes day,</l>
      <l>which you are summoned to pay:</l>
      <l>Wherefore my Author well content,</l>
      <l>because he warnes you to repent:</l>
      <l>Repentance true God doth require,</l>
      <l>it keepes you from eternall fire.</l>
   </lg>
   <trailer>FINIS.</trailer>
